I didn't wanna jinx it.
是怕坏了好事

55
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:10,380
We are pretty good at this.
我们还真会丢接球呢

56
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:14,050
We totally forgot about lunch.
我们完全忘了吃午餐

57
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:18,250
That's the first time I've ever missed a meal.
这是我第一次忘记吃饭

58
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:20,590
I think my pants are a little loose.
对，我的裤子都有点松了

59
00:03:25,130 --> 00:03:27,230
Hey,you guys. Is Monica here?
嗨，摩妮卡在吗？

60
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:31,400
I bought something. I'm not sure she'll like it.
我带了东西回来 我不确定她会喜欢

62
00:03:31,610 --> 00:03:35,510
It may seem crazy, but I've wanted this since I was a little girl.
听起有点奇怪 那个东西我从小就想要了

64
00:03:35,780 --> 00:03:37,680
You bought Shaun Cassidy!
你带的是史恩卡希迪？ （歌手）

65
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,910
No. I wish!
不是，我也希望是

66
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,480
Okay,you ready?
你们准备好了没？ 好了

67
00:03:42,255 --> 00:03:43,279
那好

68
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:47,480
Check it out.
请看！

69
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:53,650
What is it?
那是啥啊？ 

70
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:55,620
What the hell is that?
什么鬼东西？

71
00:03:57,130 --> 00:03:58,330
It's a cat.
这是猫啊

72
00:03:58,530 --> 00:03:59,860
That is not a cat!
这才不是猫

73
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:02,460
Yes,it is!
这就是猫啊

74
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,970
Why is it inside out?
它的皮怎么翻出来了？

75
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:10,210
Excuse me!
帮帮忙

76
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:14,710
But this is a purebred, show-quality sphinx cat.
这可是展示级的 纯种狮身人面猫

77
00:04:14,980 --> 00:04:17,470
How much did you pay for that?
你花了多少钱买的？

78
00:04:17,690 --> 00:04:20,020
It was extravagant, but I got a good deal.
有点奢侈 但我谈到了很好的价钱

79
00:04:20,290 --> 00:04:22,120
-How much? -Thousand bucks.
多少钱？ 一千美元

81
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,450
On a cat?
买一只猫？

82
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,160
It's not a cat!
那才不是猫！

83
00:04:30,030 --> 00:04:34,200
For a thousand dollars, you'd think at least it'd come with hair.
花一千元起码也要有毛才对

84
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,760
Or something.
或是其他有的没的

85
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,900
All right. Listen, ball boys.
你们这两个玩球的给我听好

86
00:04:39,210 --> 00:04:42,800
My grandma had one when I was little. It was the sweetest thing.
我小时候祖母就养了这种猫 它们最讨人喜欢了

87
00:04:43,010 --> 00:04:46,140
It would sit in my lap and just purr all day long.
超可爱的，躺在我的膝盖上 整天满足地喵喵叫

88
00:04:46,380 --> 00:04:49,210
I would drag a string and it would chase it.
我还会拿鞋带在地上拖 让它追着跑

89
00:04:49,450 --> 00:04:51,420
Free cats do that too, you know.
不要钱的猫也会那样

90
00:04:52,550 --> 00:04:54,110
It's not a cat!
那才不是猫！

91
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:58,180
I'm really excited about this,okay? I don't care what you think.
反正我买得很兴奋 我才不管你们怎么想

92
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:01,620
I'm gonna set up a litter box for Mrs. Whiskerson.
我要去帮威丝克森太太 张罗出一个小猫砂盒

93
00:05:03,230 --> 00:05:05,430
What am I gonna call her? Fluffy?
不然我要叫它“毛毛”吗？

94
00:05:09,470 --> 00:05:13,870
Do you wanna get something to eat, or see how long we can throw this ball?
你要去吃点东西吗？ 还是要看我们能来回丢多久？

96
00:05:15,140 --> 00:05:16,870
The ball thing.
继续丢球 是喔

97
00:05:18,410 --> 00:05:23,480
Wouldn't it be great if we could go for two hours without dropping it?
若我们连丢两小时不落地 那样是不是棒？

98
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:26,650
Yeah,it would!
对喔

99
00:05:27,890 --> 00:05:29,410
Let's do it.
来吧 好

100
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,230
I have to pee.
我要尿尿

102
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,590
And Rachel's in the bathroom!
瑞秋却在洗手间里

103
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,130
Man,I didn't think we'd make it.
没想到这样也行

104
00:05:46,770 --> 00:05:48,110
I know.
是啊

105
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:50,300
Don't switch hands, okay?
你别换手喔

106
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:01,280
Hey, ladies. What are you in here for?
小姐，你们在这里干嘛？

107
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,790
What are you doing here?
钱德，你来这里干嘛？

108
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:09,020
I am here to report a crime.
盖瑞，我是来报案的 是吗？

109
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:11,730
It's a crime that we don't spend time together.
我们俩不常聚在一起 是一种罪

110
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:12,860
What's up?
你有什么事？

111
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:18,700
You're thinking about moving in with Phoebe, and I thought we should talk.
听说你在考虑要菲比跟你同居 我心想我们或许应该聊聊

113
00:06:18,970 --> 00:06:20,200
You know,man to...
男人…

114
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,770
...well,me.
跟我的对话

115
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,200
Sure,okay.
好啊，没问题

116
00:06:24,810 --> 00:06:26,610
Are you crazy?
你在发什么神经？

117
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,270
Are you insane?
你疯了？

118
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:32,510
If you live with Phoebe,you two are gonna be living together.
若你和菲比同居 你们两个就会住在一起了

119
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:35,180
I considered that. It'd make me happy.
对，我考虑过了 我知道这会让我快乐

120
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:38,020
-You mean scared. -No,I mean happy.
你是说害怕吧 不，我是说快乐

121
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,290
Scared happy.
害怕？快乐？

123
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,160
What are you doing?
钱德，你在干嘛？

124
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,990
I'm trying to open your eyes!
我在让你张开眼睛啊 你看不出来吗？

125
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:47,000
If you live with Phoebe, she is always gonna be there.
若你和菲比同居 她就永远都会在

126
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:50,200
You get home,she's there. You go to bed, she's there.
你回家会看到她 你上床也会看到她

127
00:06:50,470 --> 00:06:53,130
You wake up and, oh, yes, she's there.
你起床呢？对，她还是在

128
00:06:53,810 --> 00:06:55,240
I know. I can't wait!
我知道，我都等不及了

129
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:59,040
Were your parents happy or something?
你父母的婚姻很幸福吧？

130
00:07:00,010 --> 00:07:03,420
I was lucky enough to find someone that I really love.
钱德，我看这件事的角度是 我很幸运能找到我的真爱

131
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,740
I just want to be around her as much as I can.
我想要尽量多跟她在一起

132
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:10,020
When you say it, it doesn't sound so scary.
怪了，这件事从你嘴里说出来 感觉就没那么恐怖了

133
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,560
You know what I'm saying?
所以你懂我的意思吧？ 

134
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,490
Yeah,I think I do.
对，我想我懂

135
00:07:13,730 --> 00:07:14,850
You know what?
这样吧

136
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:19,400
Move in with her. Move in right now. Maybe I'll move in with Monica.
跟她同居 马上就去跟她同居 或许我也应该和摩妮卡同居

137
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:22,030
No,it's too soon for you guys.
不成，你们不能操之过及

139
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,240
You're right about that.
是啊，你说的对

140
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:31,040
When they found the remains of the Mesozoic mastodon...
他们找到中生代乳齿象化石

141
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,870
...they discovered what appeared to be the remains...
却在嘴部发现到 

142
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:37,550
...of a Paleozoic amphibian in its jaws.
类似古生代两栖类的构造

143
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,850
How did it get there?
怎么会牛头不对马嘴？

144
00:07:42,890 --> 00:07:44,950
Maybe this should be more of a quiet game.
或许这个游戏应该安静一点

145
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:48,990
Hey,guys.
嗨 嗨

146
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,930
I left my watch here last night.
我昨晚把手表放在柜子上

147
00:07:51,370 --> 00:07:53,360
-lt was here. Where is it? -I don't know.
本来还在这里，到哪儿去了？ 我不知道

148
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,970
I'm late for work.
别闹了，我上班快迟到了

149
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,190
How do you know? You don't have a watch.
你怎么知道？你又没戴表

151
00:07:59,210 --> 00:08:02,940
Can you stop throwing the ball for one minute and help me find it?
能不能停一下再丢球 先帮我找表？

152
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:05,580
Oh, I don't know.... Yeah,can't do it.
不知道，没办法喔

153
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,310
-What? -Do not drop that ball.
怎样啦？怎样都好 千万别把球掉地上

155
00:08:13,550 --> 00:08:14,780
We haven't dropped it in....
我们保持球不落地已经…

156
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:16,990
Two hours,27 minutes.
2小时27分钟

157
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,830
Really?
真的啊？

158
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:22,920
I won't make it in to work today.
我今天没办法去上班 

159
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,230
I don't feel very good.
我人不太舒服

160
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:27,736
漂亮！

161
00:08:28,970 --> 00:08:32,740
For a second, I thought I was feeling better, but I'm not.
我刚才突然觉得自己好多了 但其实没有

162
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:36,440
Hey, Rach.
瑞秋 嗨

163
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:40,410
Check it out. Almost three hours without dropping it.
快来看，球不落地接近三小时

164
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:43,910
Congratulations. That's quite a waste of time.
恭喜了，真是浪费时间

165
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:48,790
You have scratches all over you.
你身上都是抓痕，怎么了？

167
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,510
Well,it's my cat.
是我的猫 

168
00:08:51,590 --> 00:08:53,790
-Oh,I got a cat. -I don't want a cat!
对了，我养了一只猫 我不想养猫

169
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:56,430
Don't worry,it's not a cat.
别担心，那不是猫 没错

171
00:08:57,500 --> 00:09:01,200
You guys,this cat is nothing like my grandmother's cat.
这只猫跟我祖母养过的猫 完全不一样

172
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,340
It's not sweet. It's not cute.
既不讨人喜欢，也不可爱

173
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:08,700
I dragged a string,and it flipped out and scratched the hell out of me.
我在地上拉着线逗它玩 它竟然发飙 把我抓得乱七八糟

175
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:14,380
I know this sounds crazy, but every time this cat hisses at me...
我知道这听来很疯狂 但我发誓 这只猫每次嘘我的时候

177
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,540
...I know it's saying,"Rachel!"
我知道它都在说“瑞秋”

178
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:26,660
Doesn't sound as crazy as paying $1000 for a cat.
花一千买美元买一只猫 比刚才那些话更疯狂

179
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:30,160
You paid $1000 for a cat when you owe me $300?
你欠我三百美元不还 还拿一千美元去买猫？

180
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:33,200
Well,I was gonna let you play with it.
我本来打算让你跟它玩的

181
00:09:36,909 --> 00:09:38,968
“中央咖啡馆”

182
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,970
Did you talk to Gary about moving in?
你跟盖瑞聊过同居的事没？

184
00:09:43,210 --> 00:09:44,870
I think you should do it.
聊过了，我觉得你应该答应

185
00:09:46,410 --> 00:09:51,220
He's a great guy and he loves you a lot. You are a very lucky lady.
他很棒，他也很爱你 你非常幸运

187
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:53,240
You are useless!
你真没用

188
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:57,890
Freaking out about commitment is the one thing you can do...
害怕承诺是你唯一会做的事

189
00:09:58,160 --> 00:10:00,090
...and you can't even do that right!
你竟然连那件事都做不好！ 天啊

190
00:10:00,330 --> 00:10:03,020
Sorry. If he asked me, I'd move in with him.
抱歉 换做我都愿意和他同居

192
00:10:06,730 --> 00:10:08,570
Get out of here,good-for-nothing.
窝囊废，你滚吧

194
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,800
Hey,Chandler.
钱德 

195
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:14,270
Hey,Gar.
盖瑞

196
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,340
Hey,sweetie.
亲爱的

197
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:19,670
Can I talk to you for a second?
能不能先聊一下？ 好啊

198
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:23,880
You look pretty today.
你今天很美

199
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,710
Thanks. Okay.
谢谢，好吧

200
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:28,280
Here's the thing.
是这样的

201
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:31,620
I really want this relationship to move forward.
我很想让这段关系更进一步

202
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:35,060
If you're not moving forward, you're moving backwards.
因为不进则退

203
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:38,270
No, if you're not moving forward, you're staying still.
不对，那不是真的 如果不进，就是静止不动

204
00:10:38,530 --> 00:10:41,370
And staying still is good. Watch this.
静止不动是很好的，你看

205
00:10:43,709 --> 00:10:45,301
菲比 是

206
00:10:45,810 --> 00:10:47,870
I want you to move in with me.
我要你搬来一起住

207
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:50,110
That is so sweet.
那真是太甜蜜了

208
00:10:50,410 --> 00:10:52,640
But don't you think it's too soon?
但你不觉得太快了些吗？

209
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:55,140
There's so much we don't know about each other.
我们彼此还有太多地方不了解

210
00:10:58,990 --> 00:11:00,820
Okay. I get it.
好吧，我懂了

211
00:11:02,290 --> 00:11:05,990
I don't want us to jump into something that we're not ready for.
我只是不希望我们操之过急 你懂吧？

212
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:12,490
I don't want to mess up what we have.
我不想搞砸我们现在的一切

213
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:16,100
I'm worried it's gonna be a big mistake.
我担心同居会铸成大错

214
00:11:16,475 --> 00:11:17,533
是啊

215
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:22,500
Which is why my answer is yes!
所以我的答案是我答应

216
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:25,410
Really?
真的吗？

217
00:11:25,650 --> 00:11:27,610
You're so happy.
我好快乐

218
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:37,780
Monica, stop throwing it so hard!
摩妮卡，别丢那么大力！

219
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,420
We're on the same team!
我们是同一队

220
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:46,160
You guys have been doing this for four hours?
四个小时？ 你们就这样丢了四小时？

221
00:11:46,370 --> 00:11:47,800
That's right,baby.
宝贝，没错

222
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:50,660
-All right. Let me in. -No,no! Don't do it!
好，让我加入 不行！…

224
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,870
What?
什么？

225
00:11:53,970 --> 00:11:55,640
He's a dropper.
他是掉球大王

226
00:11:57,610 --> 00:11:59,510
Oh,yeah. That's right!
对，没错！

227
00:11:59,850 --> 00:12:01,340
I'm not a dropper!
我才不是掉球大王

228
00:12:01,850 --> 00:12:05,010
It's really a three-person game, you know?
这其实是三个人的游戏

229
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:08,120
It's throwing and catching.
还不就是你丢我接

230
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:10,420
All right.
好吧

231
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:15,420
Oh,it's so hard.
好大力喔

232
00:12:23,140 --> 00:12:25,540
Don't worry,guys. It's not a cat.
别紧张，那不是猫喔

233
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:30,070
Oh,good God!
我的…天啊

234
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:33,540
I give up. I don't know what I'm gonna do with this thing.
我放弃了 我不知道要怎么处理

235
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:36,140
Baking it didn't help?
送它进烤箱也没用？

236
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:41,120
Take it back to where you got it.
把它送回你买的地方呢？

237
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:43,220
I tried. They won't take her back.
我试过了，他们不收

238
00:12:43,460 --> 00:12:46,890
Maybe that's because she's a minion of the Antichrist.
或许是因为它是反基督的爪牙

239
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:50,900
Why won't they take it?
瑞秋，店家为什么不收？

240
00:12:51,130 --> 00:12:53,620
They said they would only give me store credit.
他们说要收回可以 但只退我店里的购物券

241
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:57,200
What am I gonna do? Get 1000 regular cats?
我要拿来买什么？ 一千只普通的猫不成？

242
00:12:57,640 --> 00:13:01,340
You said it was a show cat. Why don't you show it,win some prize money.
你不是说这是展示猫吗？ 那就带去比赛拿奖品啊

243
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:05,240
Those shows cost a hundred bucks to enter, and all you win are these ribbons...
参加猫展要先缴一百美元 赢来的东西

245
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:08,370
...which technically belong to the damn cat.
还不是都归这死猫所有

246
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:10,950
You can keep it until you find out what to do with it.
不然你先留着罗 等到你找到处理的方法

247
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:13,550
That's not the point. I'm out $1000...
不行，那不是重点 我破费一千美元

249
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:15,250
...I'm all scratched up...
搞得全身都是抓痕

250
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:18,820
...and I'm stuck with this stupid cat that looks like a hand!
还跟长得像手的蠢猫困在一起

251
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:24,450
Oh,my God!
天啊

252
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:27,330
The cat's made my eyes water. Don't throw it to me!
那只猫害我流眼泪了 别丢球给我！

253
00:13:27,570 --> 00:13:30,230
My vision's been compromised!
我的视力被连累到了

254
00:13:31,470 --> 00:13:33,410
Oh,God! Okay.
天啊，好了…

255
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,670
It's okay. Man,that was close.
现在好了，真是惊险

256
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:39,640
Yeah,you almost overreacted to something.
是啊，你的反应也太大了点

257
00:13:43,050 --> 00:13:46,650
-We have great news. -We're moving in together. Yay!
我们有个好消息 我们要同居了，是不是很棒？

259
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:49,590
Congratulations.
恭喜… 

260
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,280
-I'm so excited! -So am l.
是啊 我好兴奋 我也是

261
00:13:51,490 --> 00:13:55,220
You're not more excited than I am. No way. I'm the most excited.
你才没有我兴奋，不可能 我是最兴奋的

262
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,330
See you at the station later.
好，晚点在局里见

263
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,500
I'll see you later. Don't forget about the moving-in!
好，晚点见 别忘了同居的事喔

264
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,730
So you're moving in with him?
你要搬去跟他住，怎么了？

265
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:07,900
I couldn't tell him no. He got so sad. Maybe it'll be all right.
我不忍心拒绝他 看他伤心成那样 或许不会有事的

267
00:14:08,410 --> 00:14:09,640
I do like him a lot...
我真的很喜欢他 

268
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:12,570
...and probably do it eventually,anyway.
同居八成也是迟早的事

269
00:14:12,850 --> 00:14:15,820
Plus,think of all the money I'll save on stamps.
想想也可以省下不少邮票钱

270
00:14:16,950 --> 00:14:18,280
Do you write him a lot?
怎么着？你常写信给他？

271
00:14:18,590 --> 00:14:20,520
I heard when people live together...
不是，只是我听说同居的人 

272
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:23,190
...they split the cost of stamps,don't they?
会分担邮票的费用，不是吗？

273
00:14:26,090 --> 00:14:27,920
-Yeah,yeah. -That's right.
是啊，没错…

274
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,330
Sorry,the oven mitts really freaked me out.
抱歉，耐热手套吓了我一跳

275
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:43,430
Hey,honey.
亲爱的

276
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,670
Did you find any apartments in Brooklyn Heights?
你找到公寓没？ 布鲁克林高地有吗？

277
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,040
No, nothing.
不，没找到

278
00:14:48,450 --> 00:14:49,540
-Oh, really? -Yeah.
真的？ 是啊

279
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,050
-Nothing at all? -No.
一间都没有？ 没有

280
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:55,350
If something opens up,we'll move in. If it has a pool. I need a pool.
只要有公寓招租 我们马上搬进去 不过要有附泳池的 我需要泳池

282
00:14:57,690 --> 00:14:59,280
Can I talk to you?
菲比，可以跟你聊一下吗？

283
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:04,690
Take a seat.
请坐 好

284
00:15:06,130 --> 00:15:07,620
You okay?
你没事吧？

285
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,530
You feel all right?
还好吧？

286
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:12,670
I feel great, because we're moving in together.
我很好啊，因为我们要同居了

287
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:14,970
So you....
那么...

288
00:15:15,210 --> 00:15:18,910
You checked the paper for listings in Brooklyn Heights,right?
报上布鲁克林高地的租屋广告 你都看过了？

289
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:21,640
You checked the Post?
邮报你有查过吗？

290
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:24,380
Yeah,there was nothing.
有啊，啥都没有

291
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:28,690
-Can I get some water? -ln a minute.
我能喝点水吗？ 等一下

292
00:15:30,490 --> 00:15:31,820
You checked today's Post?
你查过今天的邮报吗？

293
00:15:32,530 --> 00:15:34,080
Yeah,today's.
对，我是看今天的

294
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:37,490
Because this is today's Post.
这是今天的邮报

295
00:15:37,770 --> 00:15:40,170
And these are the listings I found.
我找到了这些租屋广告

296
00:15:41,070 --> 00:15:44,160
Brooklyn Heights, two bedrooms. Brooklyn Heights, one bedroom.
布鲁克林高地，两房 布鲁克林高地，一房

297
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:47,530
Brooklyn Heights,Brooklyn Heights, Brooklyn Heights!
布鲁克林高地地区…

299
00:15:48,110 --> 00:15:52,570
Oh,are these for rent? I thought people were just bragging.
这些是要租的吗？我以为他们是在 炫耀自己的房子有多棒

301
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:55,450
Let me tell you what's going on here.
我来告诉你我的想法

302
00:15:55,950 --> 00:15:57,710
Don't look at the table. Look at me.
不要看桌子，看着我

303
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:02,280
Somebody asked someone to move in with him.
一个男生要求一个女生同居

304
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:05,350
Someone said yes, but now she has doubts...
女生本来说好，现在反悔了

305
00:16:05,590 --> 00:16:09,050
...because things are moving too fast. Does that sound possible?
因为女生觉得这样太快了 你觉得是不是这样？

307
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:14,560
Yes,fine! I am someone!
对！…好，我就是那个女生

308
00:16:16,370 --> 00:16:18,770
You want me to say it? I have doubts!
你要我说老实话？ 对，我是不确定

309
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,800
I'm sorry!
对不起

310
00:16:22,114 --> 00:16:23,445
菲比？

311
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:26,310
It's okay that you feel this way.
你有这种感觉也没关系

312
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:30,450
It is soon, and there's things we don't know about each other.
这真的是很快 我们对彼此有许多地方不了解

313
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:33,150
Everything I know about you, I really like.
我只是觉得 我知道的你，我都很喜欢

314
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:37,590
Things I don't know, I'll learn in a place with our names on the mailbox.
我还不知道的你 就等同居后再慢慢了解

315
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:40,620
That's so sweet.
那样好甜蜜喔

316
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:45,900
But if it's too soon for you, we don't have to do it.
不过如果你觉得这样太快 我刚才说的可以慢慢再来 不用赶着现在就同居 

318
00:16:46,130 --> 00:16:47,960
I want you to be happy.
我只想要你快乐

319
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,430
Living with you would make me happy.
跟你同居会让我快乐的

320
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,800
You don't have to say that.
菲比，你不用那样说

321
00:16:52,070 --> 00:16:54,840
I want to live with you. I want to move in with you.
不，我很想跟你住在一起 我要跟你同居

322
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,470
Are you sure?
你确定？

323
00:16:57,410 --> 00:17:00,640
Definitely,yes! Let's live in an apartment we both live in.
对，百分之百确定！ 我们一起住在公寓同居吧

325
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:02,750
Oh,that's great.
太好了

326
00:17:03,020 --> 00:17:04,580
Oh,wait, one sec.
等等…

327
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:08,090
Hey,you! Behind the glass. Who are you looking at?
镜子后面的人 你看什么看！

329
00:17:09,290 --> 00:17:13,780
I always wanted to say that every time I was in these rooms, which was never.
我每次进来这种房间 都想说这句话 虽然我从没进来过

331
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:17,820
Show cat!
展示猫

332
00:17:18,170 --> 00:17:20,260
Quality show cat!
高级的展示猫

333
00:17:21,770 --> 00:17:23,830
-Show cat! -Oh,my God!
展示猫 天啊

334
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:26,130
What's wrong with your baby?
你的宝宝怎么了？

335
00:17:26,810 --> 00:17:28,600
That's not a baby. That's a cat.
这不是宝宝，这是猫

336
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:31,540
-It's creepy-looking. -Oh,no.
长得还真吓人 不

337
00:17:31,780 --> 00:17:35,340
It's actually very sweet. It's very sweet. Look.
它其实很讨人喜欢的… 不信你看

338
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:40,690
Yeah. Do you want it?
你要不要？

339
00:17:40,890 --> 00:17:42,290
No,I hate cats.
不了，我恨猫

340
00:17:42,490 --> 00:17:44,290
Then what are you doing to me?
那你干嘛跟我扯半天？ 

341
00:17:44,530 --> 00:17:47,550
Get out of here,all right? Move on!
滚吧，继续走你的路

342
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,690
What an unusual cat.
这只猫真不寻常

343
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:53,490
Yes,thank you! Exactly. You want it?
是的，谢谢你 真的是这样，你要吗?

345
00:17:54,130 --> 00:17:55,160
Maybe.
有可能

346
00:17:55,370 --> 00:17:58,530
I was thinking about getting a cat from the shelter,but....
我考虑要养猫 我正好要去流浪动物之家…

347
00:17:59,070 --> 00:18:02,300
-Okay. Why not? -Oh,terrific! That'll be $2,000.
好吧，就它了 太好了，总共是两千美元

349
00:18:03,810 --> 00:18:05,400
-What? -Okay,1000.
什么？ 好吧，一千

350
00:18:06,150 --> 00:18:07,840
Didn't you want me to adopt your cat?
我以为你是要我认养你的猫

352
00:18:08,050 --> 00:18:12,850
I do,but you'll have to look at this as more of an investment than a cat.
是啊，不过这不只是猫 更是一项投资

353
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:15,350
Okay,yeah. I just wanted a cat.
好吧，我要的只是猫

354
00:18:18,890 --> 00:18:23,020
Obviously,you know how to haggle, so I won't try and take you on.
你显然是杀价高手 所以我就不唬弄你了

356
00:18:23,260 --> 00:18:27,430
So $800,and I don't call the cops, because you are robbing me blind!
算你八百，我也不报警了 因为你这根本是抢劫

357
00:18:27,630 --> 00:18:31,070
Blind! Just take the cat. Leave the money. Run away!
把钱留下，猫带走 溜之大吉吧…

358
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:33,470
Run away. Damn it!
快走吧 可恶！

359
00:18:33,970 --> 00:18:37,240
Can't you at least smile or something?
死猫，你起码也笑一下嘛

360
00:18:39,910 --> 00:18:42,640
Did anybody just hear that? Anybody?
有没有人听到？谁听到了？

361
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:52,720
-I'm starving. -Come on,guys. Suck it up!
我饿死了 你们振作一点 

362
00:18:52,930 --> 00:18:54,720
We're closing in on 10 hours.
就快达成连续十小时了

363
00:18:54,930 --> 00:18:56,920
It's gut-check time!
这是比毅力的时刻

364
00:18:57,130 --> 00:19:01,300
I don't know who made you the boss. We invented this game.
怎么变成是你当老大？ 这游戏是我们发明的

365
00:19:01,740 --> 00:19:03,500
I made this game what it is!
帮帮忙，这游戏是因为我 才有现在的局面

366
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:05,570
Not fun anymore?
不再好玩的局面？

367
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,500
I'm still hungry.
我还是很饿

368
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:12,240
There's pizza at my place. We can eat with one hand. Are you with me?
好吧，我家还有一点比萨 你们可以用一手吃吧？ 要不要？

369
00:19:12,550 --> 00:19:15,140
-I am. -All right,let's go! Come on!
我要 好，我们走…

371
00:19:15,650 --> 00:19:17,240
Let's go, Team Monica!
摩妮卡大队，走罗

372
00:19:20,390 --> 00:19:22,450
We can work out the name later.
好啦，队名等一下再讨论

373
00:19:26,430 --> 00:19:28,490
What is your cat doing in my bowl?
瑞秋，你的猫在我碗里干嘛？

374
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:30,320
I'm defrosting a chicken.
不是啦，我在解冻鸡肉

375
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,660
I sold Mrs. Whiskerson.
我把威丝克森太太卖掉了

376
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:36,560
Thank God!
谢天谢地

377
00:19:36,940 --> 00:19:39,340
-Get your money back? -Yeah,$1500.
你的钱拿回来没？ 有，一千五百美元

379
00:19:39,610 --> 00:19:41,630
You made a profit?
哇，你还有赚耶

380
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:47,610
I just came for the red velvet pillow.
我是来拿红丝绒枕头的

382
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:51,010
-There you go. -Thanks,Rachel.
在这里 瑞秋，谢了

383
00:19:51,290 --> 00:19:54,250
Don't forget, you can come visit her anytime.
别忘了，你随时可以来看它

384
00:19:54,450 --> 00:19:57,080
Oh, good. Great. I'll keep that in mind.
好…我会记得的

385
00:20:01,630 --> 00:20:04,150
So is this some kind of snake or something?
这是啥？某种蛇吗？

386
00:20:15,710 --> 00:20:17,300
I like waking up with you.
我真喜欢和你一起醒来 

387
00:20:17,510 --> 00:20:20,110
I like waking up with you too.
我也是

388
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:23,210
Oh, it's such a beautiful morning.
今天早上真美

389
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,880
I could stay here all day.
我可以在床上待一整天

390
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:26,950
That would be great.
那样不错

391
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:30,850
-We could have breakfast in bed. -Wait,just a second.
我们可以在床上吃早餐 等等 好

393
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,450
Oh,no.
不会吧

394
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:42,160
All right. Come on, Monica! Look alive. Come on!
来，摩妮卡，活力点… 

396
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:53,910
Oh,I was having the best dream.
我刚才做了最棒的梦 

397
00:20:54,050 --> 00:20:56,070
-What? -I dreamed I was drowning...
什么梦？ 我梦到自己溺水 

398
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:58,740
...and not throwing this ball.
不用再丢这颗球了

399
00:21:01,190 --> 00:21:02,680
Oh, good. You're all up.
很好，你们都起床了

400
00:21:03,090 --> 00:21:06,360
It's 6:00 in the morning. Why aren't you at Gary's?
菲比，现在才早上六点 你怎么没在盖瑞那里？

401
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:08,260
-Oh, yeah. That's over. -What?
对，结束了 什么？

402
00:21:08,530 --> 00:21:11,460
Gary's such a great guy. You can work it out.
别这样，盖瑞这么好 有什么问题都能解决的

403
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:13,690
-He shot a bird. -That is over.
他开枪杀了一只鸟 结束了

404
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:17,030
-I'm sorry. -That's terrible.
太糟糕了…我很遗撼…

405
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:18,740
Are you okay?
菲比，你还好吧？

406
00:21:18,870 --> 00:21:20,400
I'll be all right.
对…我不会有事的

407
00:21:21,140 --> 00:21:23,170
Here,Phoebe.
菲比，接住

408
00:21:23,310 --> 00:21:24,370
I don't feel like playing.
我不太想玩球

409
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:32,410
It's okay. It's okay.
没事…

410
00:21:33,320 --> 00:21:36,380
It didn't happen. No one needs to know.
就当没发生这件事 没必要让别人知道

411
00:21:36,590 --> 00:21:38,790
She's not an official ball player.
菲比又不是正式的队员 

412
00:21:38,990 --> 00:21:41,720
Only official ball players can drop the ball.
正式队员掉球才算数

413
00:21:43,130 --> 00:21:44,220
-Come on. -Let's go.
算了…我好饿…

414
00:21:45,770 --> 00:21:47,320
You wanna get breakfast?
菲比，要吃早餐吗？ 

415
00:21:47,630 --> 00:21:49,400
Okay, let's race!
好，我们来赛跑

416
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,630
First one there wins.
最先到的赢

417
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:55,940
You guys wanna eat here?
你们要在这里吃吗？ 

418
00:22:01,780 --> 00:22:02,870
That was great,huh?
在这里就好

419
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:05,210
Can you believe how long we threw it?
真不敢相信我们丢了那么久

420
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:07,550
It is amazing it lasted that long.
是啊，撑了那么久 真的很不可思议

421
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:09,520
My arm is killing me.
是啊，我的手臂酸死了

422
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:12,350
No, I meant with the dropper over here.
不是，我是说有掉球高手在 还能那么久

423
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:14,890
How did I get this reputation as a dropper?
“掉球高手”这称号 怎么会落到我头上？

424
00:22:15,100 --> 00:22:17,330
I am anything but a dropper.
我再怎么说也不是掉球高手

425
00:22:17,530 --> 00:22:19,020
Ross!
罗斯…

426
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000


427
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
